Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:20.27,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}'Cause you're my only star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:26.08,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I wonder why my tears come at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:29.52,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Calling you, so like a little child
